text: A failed coup d'état happened in Guinea-Bissau on 1 February 2022. Gunfire was heard coming from the government house in Bissau. A few hours later, president Umaro Sissoco Embalo said the coup over, he said that "many" members of the security forces had been killed in a "failed attack against democracy." ==References== Category:2022 in Africa Category:Coups d'état Category:February 2022 events 2022 coup d'état attempt
title: 2022 Guinea-Bissau coup d'état attempt
